   Updated     : 2026-03-23
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Purpose     : Demo page for the FrameworkV2 TableV2 component family.
                 Route: /v2/demo/table
                 Uses generic/sample data - no Absence-specific modules.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-21  Initial implementation.
     - 1.1.0  2026-03-23  Wrapped content in PageTemplateV2 to restore V2 chrome
                           (header, sidebar) after MainLayoutV2 was made body-only.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Notes       :
     None.
